Package Entity.Food

Class FoodItem

java.lang.Object
Entity.Food.FoodItem
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFoodItem, Serializable
public class FoodItem extends Object implements IFoodItem, Serializable
Represents a food item in the system. Implements the IFoodItem interface and provides details such as name, price, branch, and item type.
